  playerStats: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b7d3c9e7f6c33844e81cb8cbf5f34e55, type: 2}
  title: Who claims the people cannot laugh during a mass? Summon the finest comedian
    from our ranks, we shall entertain the masses!
  description: 'COST: No cost'
