    - rid: 1516066228257685603
      type: {class: WeighedChoice, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        modules:
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 1516066228257685604
          - rid: 1516066228257685605
          statUsed: 0
          output: 'The crowd roars with laughter at our man''s performance. However,
            our sacred teachings are entirely lost in the absurdist sea of his creation.
            At the very least, we have ensured the people will desire to return.

            [Gained
            20 Flock & 30 Zeal]

'
        - weight: 30
          module:
          - rid: 1516066228257685606
          statUsed: 0
          output: 'A difficult audience... the jests do not seem to land. By the
            conclusion of the service, half the temple stands empty, and our man
            is red as a turnip from sheer embarrassment.

            [Lost 10 Zeal]

'
        - weight: 20
          module:
          - rid: 1516066228257685607
          - rid: 1516066228257685608
          statUsed: 1
          output: 'What an artisan! Our man is a natural comedian. Not only that,
            but while it would be simple to merely make the masses laugh and leave
            it at that, he masterfully weaves reflections and holy lessons between
            every jest, causing the populace to pay closer attention than ever before!

            [Gained
            30 Flock & 60 Zeal]

'
